Package: MNLM
Type: Package
Title: Generating Multiple Correlated Neutral Landscape Models
Version: 1.0
Authors@R: person("Ian", "Wang", email = "ianwang@berkeley.edu",
                  role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: A toolkit for generating sets of neutral landscape models (NLMs) with specified correlations. NLMs can be generated using a variety of algorithms, and the spatial structure of the NLMs are maintained while generating additional raster surfaces with user-specified correlations.
